import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Typography,
  Container,
  Paper,
  Grid,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  Chip,
  Avatar,
  LinearProgress,
} from '@mui/material';
import {
  School,
  LocationOn,
  CalendarToday,
  EmojiEvents,
  Code,
  Psychology,
} from '@mui/icons-material';

const About = () => {
  const stats = [
    { number: '50+', label: 'Projects Completed', icon: <Code /> },
    { number: '3+', label: 'Years Learning', icon: <School /> },
    { number: '10+', label: 'Technologies', icon: <Psychology /> },
  ];

  const interests = [
    { name: '🚀 Space Technology', color: 'primary' },
    { name: '🤖 AI & Machine Learning', color: 'secondary' },
    { name: '🎮 Game Development', color: 'primary' },
    { name: '📱 Mobile Apps', color: 'secondary' },
    { name: '🌐 Web Development', color: 'primary' },
    { name: '📊 Data Science', color: 'secondary' },
  ];

  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ py: 8 }}>
      {/* Header */}
      <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', mb: 6 }}>
        <Typography
          variant="h2"
          sx={{
            mb: 2,
            background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #4dabf7)',
            backgroundClip: 'text',
            WebkitBackgroundClip: 'text',
            WebkitTextFillColor: 'transparent',
            position: 'relative',
            '&::after': {
              content: '""',
              position: 'absolute',
              bottom: -10,
              left: '50%',
              transform: 'translateX(-50%)',
              width: 60,
              height: 4,
              background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #4dabf7, #f50057)',
              borderRadius: 2,
            },
          }}
        >
          About Me
        </Typography>
        <Typography
          variant="h6"
          sx={{ color: 'text.secondary', maxWidth: 600, mx: 'auto' }}
        >
          Get to know me better
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Grid container spacing={4}>
        {/* Left Column */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          {/* Journey Card */}
          <Card sx={{ mb: 3, height: 'fit-content' }}>
            <CardContent sx={{ p: 3 }}>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                <EmojiEvents sx={{ color: 'primary.main', mr: 1 }} />
                <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 600 }}>
                  My Journey
                </Typography>
              </Box>
              <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ mb: 2, lineHeight: 1.6 }}>
                I'm a passionate Computer Science student with a love for creating 
                innovative solutions through code. My journey in tech started with 
                curiosity about how software works, and has evolved into a deep 
                appreciation for clean code, user experience, and problem-solving.
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ lineHeight: 1.6 }}>
                Currently pursuing my degree in Computer Science, I'm constantly 
                learning new technologies and applying them to real-world projects. 
                I believe in the power of technology to make a positive impact on 
                people's lives.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>

          {/* Stats */}
          <Grid container spacing={2}>
            {stats.map((stat, index) => (
              <Grid item xs={12} sm={4} key={index}>
                <Card
                  sx={{
                    textAlign: 'center',
                    transition: 'transform 0.3s ease',
                    '&:hover': {
                      transform: 'translateY(-5px)',
                    },
                  }}
                >
                  <CardContent>
                    <Box sx={{ color: 'primary.main', mb: 1 }}>
                      {stat.icon}
                    </Box>
                    <Typography
                      variant="h4"
                      sx={{
                        fontWeight: 700,
                        background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #4dabf7, #f50057)',
                        backgroundClip: 'text',
                        WebkitBackgroundClip: 'text',
                        WebkitTextFillColor: 'transparent',
                        mb: 0.5,
                      }}
                    >
                      {stat.number}
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: 'text.secondary' }}>
                      {stat.label}
                    </Typography>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        </Grid>

        {/* Right Column */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          {/* Profile Card */}
          <Card sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
            <CardContent sx={{ p: 3, textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Avatar
                sx={{
                  width: 150,
                  height: 150,
                  mx: 'auto',
                  mb: 2,
                  background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #4dabf7, #f50057)',
                  fontSize: '3rem',
                }}
              >
                📸
              </Avatar>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 600, mb: 1 }}>
                Computer Science Student
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', mb: 1 }}>
                <LocationOn sx={{ fontSize: 20, mr: 0.5, color: 'text.secondary' }} />
                <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: 'text.secondary' }}>
                  Your City, Country
                </Typography>
              </Box>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', mb: 1 }}>
                <School sx={{ fontSize: 20, mr: 0.5, color: 'text.secondary' }} />
                <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: 'text.secondary' }}>
                  University Name
                </Typography>
              </Box>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
                <CalendarToday sx={{ fontSize: 20, mr: 0.5, color: 'text.secondary' }} />
                <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: 'text.secondary' }}>
                  Expected Graduation: 2025
                </Typography>
              </Box>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>

          {/* Interests */}
          <Card>
            <CardContent sx={{ p: 3 }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 600, mb: 2, textAlign: 'center' }}>
                Interests & Hobbies
              </Typography>
              <Box
                sx={{
                  display: 'flex',
                  flexWrap: 'wrap',
                  gap: 1,
                  justifyContent: 'center',
                }}
              >
                {interests.map((interest, index) => (
                  <Chip
                    key={index}
                    label={interest.name}
                    color={interest.color}
                    variant="filled"
                    sx={{
                      fontWeight: 500,
                      transition: 'transform 0.3s ease',
                      '&:hover': {
                        transform: 'scale(1.05)',
                      },
                    }}
                  />
                ))}
              </Box>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default About;
